<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ ài zuì zhǎng jiǔ 迦南169</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ ài zuì wěi dà zhǔ ài zuì shēn hòu
 zhǔ ài zuì měi shàn zhǔ ài zuì zhǎng jiǔ
 nǐ ruò jīn shēng dé dào tā biàn shuō cǐ shì wú ài mù
 nǐ ruò jīn shēng yōng yǒu tā biàn shuō cǐ shì wú suǒ qiú
 rú tóng kū mù féng chūn fā xīn yá
 yòu rú jiǔ hàn de tǔ de biàn lǜ zhōu
 nǐ wèn zhǔ ài duō shēn duō zhǎng jiǔ
 tiān de fèi qù zhǔ ài yǒng cún liú.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>169</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>